    "html": "Paakkari, L. and R. V\u00e4limaa (2013): <strong>Ethical issues in the teaching and learning of health topics in schools: The conceptions of teacher trainees</strong>. <em>Teaching and Teacher Education</em> 34. 66-76. ",
