    "html": "Fredlund, C., F. Svensson, C. Svedin, G. Priebe, and M. Wadsby (2013): <strong>Adolescents\u2019 lifetime experience of selling sex: Development over five years</strong>. <em>Journal of Child Sexual Abuse</em> 22.3. 312-325. ",
    "bibtex": "@article{Fredlund.2013,\n    abstract = {Lifetime experience of selling sex among adolescents was investigated together with sociodemographic correlates, parent-child relationship, and the existence of people to confide in. Changes over time regarding the selling of sex were investigated through a comparison of data from 2004 and 2009. This study was carried out using 3,498 adolescents from a representative sample of Swedish high school students with a mean age 18.3 years. Of these adolescents, 1.5{\\%} stated that they had given sexual services for reimbursement and both male and female buyers existed. The adolescents who had sold sex had a poorer parent-child relationship during childhood and had fewer people to confide in about problems and worries. Changes over time were found especially regarding the Internet as a contact source and also immigrant background.},\n    author = {Fredlund, Cecilia and Svensson, Frida and Svedin, Carl Goran and Priebe, Gisela and Wadsby, Marie},\n    year = {2013},\n    title = {Adolescents' lifetime experience of selling sex: Development over five years},\n    keyword = {Emigrants and Immigrants/psychology/statistics {\\&} numerical data;Female;Global Health;Humans;Jugendliche und junge Erwachsene;Male;Parent-Child Relations;Sex Work/psychology/statistics {\\&} numerical data;Sexual Behavior/psychology/statistics {\\&} numerical data;Social Support;Students/psychology/statistics {\\&} numerical data;Surveys and Questionnaires;Sweden/ethnology;Time Factors},\n    pages = {312--325},\n    volume = {22},\n    number = {3},\n    issn = {1053-8712},\n    journal = {Journal of Child Sexual Abuse},\n    doi = {10.1080/10538712.2013.743950}\n}",
